{"tid":1436721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少女在天水圍被捕時疑走光　憶述遭警腳踢及以警棍棒打","createTime":"2019-08-09T10:43:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T10:50:20.000Z","uid":41404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb966f0899d283545e07d994b859662b968ac94","tid":1436721,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:43:07.000Z","msg":"剛過去的星期日晚，有市民發起包圍天水圍警署行動，一名少女被捕時疑似走光。她以化名Chloe接受本台訪問，對於警方曾於簡報會聲稱先由女警制服她不果，才有男警增援，Chloe表示並非事實。<br />\n<br />\n她憶述自己當晚隔著馬路指罵警署的警員，不久有防暴警察出動，她隨即被捕，罪名是非法集結，而非簡報會提及的襲警，暫時未有被正式落案起訴。<br />\n<br />\nChloe表示，在拘捕行動中她先被6至7名男性防暴警察按在地上，對方用腳踢她、用警棍打她，又以粗口辱罵她。她被箍頸後雙手被扣上膠索帶，然後被抬往警署，途中她不斷呼喊「女警」、「記者」，幾分鐘後她用力掙脫，跌倒地上，之後才有女警出現。<br />\n<br />\nChloe憶述，當晚她身穿及膝連身裙，被警員抬起時意識到裙子被掀起，內褲有移位，一度嘗試用手按著裙子；但由於情況太混亂，無法確定內褲有沒有鬆脫。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，在警署內被防暴警察推倒地上，面向天花，有軍裝男警員對她叉頸，亦有女警向她作出人身攻擊，警員更拒絕出示委任證。"},{"pid":"18426fb191be28bc599f83de22751c3764c229c1","tid":1436721,"uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:43:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473679-20190809.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473679-20190809.htm&d=mdS8n1K3gC4RK9SJ0KjOq0YZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=7876cc2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473679-20190809.htm&h=fc1481c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473679-20190809.htm</a>"},{"pid":"17b6241a28765b55002c88e48590b0e0e1591d0b","tid":1436721,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:43:54.000Z","msg":"【和你飛】機場集會文宣資源集合<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dzJpkT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dzJpkT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cd7025ab6140949bee9f2830939d1ca6b444de95","tid":1436721,"uid":52705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:45:22.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警OT，老婆3P<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db432dda70ba2b4d524c570e1916e5ea7cbc60d","tid":1436721,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1ce0250371cb808c161a31ac59d5c023260bef","tid":1436721,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:50:20.000Z","msg":"人在做，天在看"}]}